datamap-ve-skip:
Label of the skip button in bottom-right corner of the dialog, used to skip the process and go straight to the source editor.
{{Identical|Skip}}
datamap-vec-intro: Text shown before the creation form, in the dialog.
datamap-vec-crs-top-left: Coordinate system origin point option. The dropdown's label is {{mw-msg|datamap-vec-select-crs-origin}}.
datamap-vec-crs-bottom-left: Coordinate system origin point option. The dropdown's label is {{mw-msg|datamap-vec-select-crs-origin}}.
datamap-vec-error-bad-file-type: Typ souboru ($1) není podporován; zvolte prosím soubor JPEG, PNG, GIF nebo SVG.
datamap-vec-error-poor-file-type: Tento typ souboru může v omezených sítích fungovat špatně. Používejte JPEGy, kdykoli je to možné.
datamap-vec-submit:
Label of the button to proceed to the source editor, with a preset generated from user's data.
{{Identical|Proceed}}
datamap-vec-example-group-id:
ID of the default, example marker group. Do not use spaces. This will appear in the generated source code.
{{Identical|Example}}
datamap-vec-example-group-name: Name of the default, example marker group. This will appear in the generated source code.
datamap-vec-example-marker: Name of the default, example marker. This will appear in the generated source code.
